  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- This is a platform action game where you aim to reach the top of the stage.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430790/extras/15b3c8a0000a50ab7853e01154bb6a51.webp?t=1762907222\" width=32 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- An adventure spanning 12 stages. <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430790/extras/963cdfef5b705ed7c42084b98fc83be6.webp?t=1762907222\" width=32 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Throw bombs to defeat enemies. <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430790/extras/003795b3ebbe7c2e9cb2daa44e104671.webp?t=1762907222\" width=31 height=31 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Climb the construction site towards the red flag. <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430790/extras/05d3acedc5cfcad994cc5bcf4a819520.webp?t=1762907222\" width=32 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Get a burger, fries and a drink to earn bonus scores.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430790/extras/6a07c002eed9342618fe5083a4685115.webp?t=1762907222\" width=30 height=30 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430790/extras/270d0402e31687a45165ff1e9b74a867.webp?t=1762907222\" width=30 height=30 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430790/extras/7ea9cc43e862a5174c24c7281a8b8be0.webp?t=1762907222\" width=30 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  When you reach 10,000 points, your stock will increase by one. <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430790/extras/36647a65d9f2ee7e6041c003349e07e6.webp?t=1762907222\" width=30 height=14 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Enemies... Avoid getting hit by birds, wheels, or spikes.  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430790/extras/226643de9ed39c198a2a47a113d5ee5e.webp?t=1762907222\" width=30 height=30 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430790/extras/cfac1564e7a50413dd6b6900990096cf.webp?t=1762907222\" width=30 height=30 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430790/extras/3bf4d2290227708e394ba78772658570.webp?t=1762907222\" width=30 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430790/extras/7adc0871419860eb6d0be66544714038.webp?t=1762907222\" width=32 height=32 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430790/extras/486c6b3c6b5413a28747e4efa5f5f7ef.webp?t=1762907222\" width=32 height=32 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430790/extras/15b3c8a0000a50ab7853e01154bb6a51.webp?t=1762907222\" width=32 height=32 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_im